sub_title: Outdoor Instructor, Farmer, Carpenter and Business Development
summary: Bachelor graduate in International Business Administration. Changed my direction from office environment to the outdoor with special affiliation to working with people and nature. My goal is to develop in the outdoor and seek new learning experiences and challenges abroad, which I find brings me more satisfaction in life. No matter the next step, if there are fruits of learning to be picked there is a potential for me.
